PN,36401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775664666
OL,3,C342 dog thefts, not one conviction
OL,5,FNo-one has been convicted following
OL,6,Fmore than 340 dog thefts in West
OL,7,FYorkshire in the last three years,
OL,8,Ffigures obtained by ITV Calendar show.
OL,10,FA freedom of information request
OL,11,Frevealed 342 crimes were recorded by
OL,12,FWest Yorkshire Police from 2023 to
OL,13,F2025, but none was successfully
OL,14,Fprosecuted.
OL,16,FOne dog owner told Calendar police are
OL,17,Ffailing to act on evidence.
OL,19,FWest Yorkshire Police said it took all
OL,20,Freports seriously and was using recent
OL,21,Flegislation to increase prosecutions.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
