FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775664666
OL,3,C342 dog thefts, not one conviction
OL,5,F'There is no pain like it'
OL,7,FEwa Hunt's dogs Molly and Bruno were
OL,8,Fstolen from her home in Featherstone,
OL,9,Fnear Wakefield, in February last year.
OL,11,FDoorbell camera footage showed the
OL,12,Fthief walking off with the dogs under
OL,13,Fcover of darkness.
OL,15,FWatching it was "like being stabbed in
OL,16,Fthe heart" Ms Hunt said.
OL,18,F"There is no pain like it," she said.
OL,19,F"They're my best friends.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775664666
OL,3,C342 dog thefts, not one conviction
OL,5,F"I've had Molly since she was eight
OL,6,Fweeks old, I watched her give birth to
OL,7,Fall the puppies. I never imagined I
OL,8,Fwould feel such a bond with any pet,
OL,9,Flike I have done with these three dogs.
OL,11,F"I didn't have to think about leaving
OL,12,Fthem in the house when I nipped to the
OL,13,Fshops or went out for a couple of
OL,14,Fhours in the evening.
OL,16,F"Now I have to think every single day,
OL,17,Fevery single minute, what I'm doing,
OL,18,Fwhere I'm going. Who is looking after
OL,19,Fthe dogs."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775664666
OL,3,C342 dog thefts, not one conviction
OL,5,FOne of the dogs was later found, but
OL,6,Fthe other is still missing.
OL,8,FMs Hunt, who has a third dog, added:
OL,9,F"I still live with the threat of the
OL,10,Fother two still being taken."
OL,12,FDespite the footage, no-one has been
OL,13,Fconvicted over the incident.
OL,15,FThe figures obtained by Calendar show
OL,16,Fthat less than one per cent of cases
OL,17,Fin the last decade have resulted in
OL,18,Fsuccessful court action.
OL,20,FMs Hunt said she felt "totally fobbed
OL,21,Foff" by police for the last 12 months.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775664666
OL,3,C342 dog thefts, not one conviction
OL,5,F"There have been many, many missed
OL,6,Fopportunities," she added.
OL,8,F"Right from day one they could have
OL,9,Fretrieved CCTV, they could have acted
OL,10,Fon evidence that we gave them, and
OL,11,Fthey haven't. And they've been very,
OL,12,Fvery slow on the things they have
OL,13,Facted on. So I feel very, very let
OL,14,Fdown by the police.
OL,16,F"They're not acting on evidence,
OL,17,Fthey're not acting quick enough. It's
OL,18,Fjust enabling the thieves to carry on."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775664666
OL,3,C342 dog thefts, not one conviction
OL,5,FFormer dog trainer Ryan O'Meara, who
OL,6,Fco-founded dog rescue organisation
OL,7,FDogs Blog, said: "When somebody steals
OL,8,Fa dog, they are effectively committing
OL,9,Fa crime that has such a huge emotional
OL,10,Fimpact on the victim. It is time, in
OL,11,Fmy opinion, that it is taken much more
OL,12,Fseriously."
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire Police said it
OL,15,Frecognised "the distress the theft of
OL,16,Fpets can cause to victims".
OL,18,FSupt Alan Travis said extensive
OL,19,Fenquiries were carried out into the
OL,20,Ftheft of Ms Hunt's dogs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775664666
OL,3,C342 dog thefts, not one conviction
OL,5,FHe added: "A man was arrested on
OL,6,Fsuspicion of burglary but, despite
OL,7,Fconsultation with the Crown
OL,8,FProsecution Service, it was not
OL,9,Fthought there was sufficient evidence
OL,10,Ffor charges to be brought.
OL,12,F"The investigation remained subject to
OL,13,Freview by senior officers, and it was
OL,14,Fconcluded that while some
OL,15,Finvestigative opportunities were
OL,16,Fregrettably missed, all reasonable
OL,17,Flines of enquiry were still followed."
OL,26,@mD@KOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
