OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775664666
OL,3,C342 dog thefts, not one conviction
OL,5,FIn a separate statement, the force
OL,6,Fsaid it took all reports of theft
OL,7,Fseriously and would "investigate these
OL,8,Fmatters to identify suspects where
OL,9,Fthere are lines of enquiry available".
OL,11,FIt added: "We recognise the distress
OL,12,Foften caused by the theft of a pet and
OL,13,Fare using recent legislation under The
OL,14,FPet Abduction Act 2024 to increase
OL,15,Fprosecutions in cases where suspects
OL,16,Fare identified."
OL,26,@sD@KOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
